</blockquote></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wezloc>Wezloc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 10:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8323.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cyas</span><hr size=1> The moderation is major heavy these days. I read the boards alot less now. I vist every couple of days. General is so blame that I take a glance then head to some other website. The discussion, and heat that use to make this board great has all bud died. The truth is very few people are visiting or posting on the board anymore because everything gets tossed into forum that like 2 people read/post in per week. There are far to many forums.<br>
