Wezloc <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cyricusbloodbane>Cyricus Bloodbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1352<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 10:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8323.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://520013139003-001.bei.t-online.de/IWD_Human_Male_Wizard3.gif height=58 width=36></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cyas</span><hr size=1> Heh, i know that a lot of people (including myself) wanted to reduce the number of forums a while back. It was decided then that we still need a epic pet forum, a epic quest forum, a pet forum, a quest forum, 14 forums just for levelling purpose etc. <br>
<br>
